com.interpss.core.acsc.fault

Interface AcscBusFault

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusRef<BaseAcscBus<?,?>>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AcscBranchFault, DStabBranchFault
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcscBranchFaultImpl, AcscBusFaultImpl, DStabBranchFaultImpl

    public interface AcscBusFault
extends BusRef<BaseAcscBus<?,?>>
    A representation of the model object 'Bus Fault'. A class to describe a bus fault. The fault id = busId+faultCode.

    The following features are supported:

    • Fault Type
    • Fault Code
    • ZLG Fault
    • ZLL Fault
    • Fault Result
    See Also:
    AcscFaultPackage.getAcscBusFault()
